### Get all shift weeks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks
Accept: application/json

### Get single shift week
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new shift week
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "start_date": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2024-01-21T23:59:59Z",
    "department_id": 1,
    "status": "planned",
    "notes": "Regular week"
}

### Update shift week
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "start_date": "2024-01-22T00:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2024-01-28T23:59:59Z",
    "department_id": 1,
    "status": "confirmed",
    "notes": "Updated schedule"
}

### Delete shift week
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks/1
Accept: application/json

### Get shift weeks by department
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shiftweeks/department/1
Accept: application/json
